com.tinfoil.sms.settings

Class EditNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • Activity
      • com.tinfoil.sms.settings.EditNumber

  • public class EditNumber
extends Activity
    TODO add remove initiator flag. An activity used to edit a single number from a given contact. This activity returns a AddContact.RESULT_CODE if changes have been made and the list needs to be update, else returns default result code. The Extras are included are: EditNumber.UPDATE, whether the number has been updated or not EditNumber.NUMBER, the number that has been edited AddContact.POSITION, the position of the given number in the contact's numbers array list, -1 if it is a new number EditNumber.ADD, whether the number is to update or deleted
